title: Riot 10th Anniversary Skin - Not received?
body:
I haven't received the Riot Games 10th anniversary gift yet. I received the icon, and already own Riot Kayle, but haven't received the mystery gift. Have the dates been pushed back?

Please Help

replies.body: I havent yet either, havent heard anything about it yet
You received Riot Kayle on the 15th of September!  Hope that helps clear things up!
I looked into this for you and see you already received a Mystery Gift for the anniversary present on the 19th of September.  Looks like Pool Party Miss Fortune!  Congrats!
